, and this sure isn't going to help:<br>
<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.mouseplanet.com/david/dk030814.htm">www.mouseplanet.com/david/dk030814.htm</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
<br>
Not that I'm a big Disney fan or anything, but let's face it, they're the most powerful and influential company when it comes to 2D movies. If they're getting out of it, and focusing on 3D now, then that's pretty much it. Sure, there have been a few 2D movies here and there that weren't done by Disney, but most of them bombed, whether they were good or not. <p><html>
